---
config:
  layout: elk
---
flowchart TB
    Interface["Interface Layer<br>(src/interface)"] -- Invokes Use Cases --> Application["Application Layer<br>(src/app)"]
    Application -- Coordinates --> Domain["Domain Layer<br>(src/domain)"]
    Application -- Uses Types/Utils --> Shared["Shared Layer<br>(src/shared)"]
    Domain -- Uses Types/Utils --> Shared
    Infrastructure["Infrastructure Layer<br>(src/infra)"] -- Implements Ports &amp; Adapters --> Application
    Infrastructure -- Implements Repositories --> Domain
    Interface -- Uses Configuration --> Infrastructure

     Interface:::layerBox
     Application:::layerBox
     Domain:::layerBox
     Shared:::layerBox
     Infrastructure:::layerBox
    classDef layerBox fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px